llars to anything, animate or inanimate, located thereon or therein commits a serious misdemeanor.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{3.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A person who knowingly trespasses on the property of another with the intent to commit a hate crime, as defined in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 729A.2}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, commits a serious misdemeanor.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{4.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A person committing a trespass as defined in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 716.7}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ with the intent to commit a hate crime which results in injury to any person or damage in an amount more than three hundred dollars to anything, animate or inanimate, located thereon or therein commits an aggravated misdemeanor.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{5.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A person who commits a trespass while hunting, other than hunting a farm deer as defined in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 170.1}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ or preserve whitetail as defined in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 484C.1}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, commits a simple misdemeanor punishable as a scheduled violation under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 805.8C, subsection 12}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{. A peace officer shall consider arresting and may arrest the person under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 805.9, subsection 3}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, paragraph }}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\u8220\'3fc\u8221\'3f}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, if the person refuses to leave the property after receiving a citation or immediately returns to the property after receiving a citation, or may arrest the person as otherwise provided under law. Th